291
00:27:02,737 --> 00:27:04,572
Tu as eu ta réunion ?

292
00:27:04,989 --> 00:27:06,074
Oui.

293
00:27:07,367 --> 00:27:09,744
Il pense que j'ai mes chances à Huntington.

294
00:27:11,579 --> 00:27:12,664
Évidemment.

295
00:27:13,456 --> 00:27:16,376
